data.description: Option to assume a 2.99% interest. This is a single-family home built in 2020, located in the JB Ranch 55+ community. This residence features a total living area of 2,032 square feet on a 7,405 square foot lot, with a total building area of 2,641 square feet.  The architectural style of the house is Craftsman, and it is constructed with block, concrete, and stucco materials. It has a shingle roof and its foundation is also made of block. Inside, the home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The flooring is a mix of carpet and ceramic tile. Among the interior features are ceiling fans, crown molding, custom trim throughout, a kitchen/family room combo, solid surface counters, and a split bedroom design. The home is equipped with central air for cooling and central heating.  For parking, the property includes a garage that can accommodate 2 vehicles. The exterior features of the home include an irrigation system, rain gutters, and a sidewalk.  The homeowners' association (HOA) provides several amenities such as a clubhouse, pickleball courts, pool, tennis courts, and also covers maintenance grounds, recreational facilities, and trash services. The monthly HOA fee is $179.  In terms of utilities, the property is connected to a public sewer and water source, and cable is available.  The local area is described as having a medium noise level and is car-dependent with a Walk Score® of 28, indicating some bikeability. The property is in close proximity to various amenities including groceries, restaurants, and a park.
